cast.name: 朱利安·阿桑奇 Julian Assange
丹尼尔·多姆沙伊特·伯格 Daniel Domscheit-Berg

trans_title: 维基解密：战争、谎言和录像带
introduction: A documentary special which investigates the website that has given rise to one of the greatest controversies of the last decade. From the site's inception through to the current allegations, this revealing documentary follows the story of the charismatic founder of the website - Julian Assange. Assange is exclusively interviewed for the film about the motives behind the WikiLeaks organisation and the impact it has had around the globe.
